    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is this game about?</strong></h2>Explore the cursed dungeon of <strong>Innkeeper's Basement</strong> in this minesweeper-inspired roguelite: Use cards from your deck to destroy enemies, interact with special objects and journey deeper on the increasingly difficult levels!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/0fde8782b7e7b95406c326fad317228b.poster.avif?t=1739825521\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/0fde8782b7e7b95406c326fad317228b.webm?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/0fde8782b7e7b95406c326fad317228b.mp4?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inspired by</h2>Slay the Spire, Runestone Keeper, Desktop Dungeons &amp; Minesweeper, among others.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to play?</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First, create your Character...</h2>Try over <strong>5100</strong> character combinations, each one with a different starting deck, stats, buffs and / or debuffs!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/4c02098ed9b8e12d3a604c71e180f3ea.poster.avif?t=1739825521\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/4c02098ed9b8e12d3a604c71e180f3ea.webm?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Next, select the Dungeon...</h2>Choose one of the 12 unique Dungeons, each one with different goals!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/20956bef3c215552b62402a23fb1f8c7.poster.avif?t=1739825521\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/20956bef3c215552b62402a23fb1f8c7.webm?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/20956bef3c215552b62402a23fb1f8c7.mp4?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...and start your Adventure! :)</h2>With minesweeper-inspired exploration! :)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/ce298fa51928c6f8e0c9c42512e4b510.poster.avif?t=1739825521\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/ce298fa51928c6f8e0c9c42512e4b510.webm?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/ce298fa51928c6f8e0c9c42512e4b510.mp4?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2>Mouse is all you need to play the game. Use &quot;WSAD&quot; for easier navigation and hotkeys below the cards (1,2,3,4...) for faster gameplay!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build up your deck as you play!</strong></h2>Every run will give you new cards and items to modify your deck and stats / buffs during gameplay!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/1aec2d4da629bd74a65bb8a7047586ec.poster.avif?t=1739825521\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/1aec2d4da629bd74a65bb8a7047586ec.webm?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/1aec2d4da629bd74a65bb8a7047586ec.mp4?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Oh, the game also has *Tons* of unlocks...</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 13+ Dungeons<br></li><li> 16+ Character Races<br></li><li> 24+ Character Classes <br></li><li> 10+ Constellations<br></li><li> many Cards, Enemies and other in-game elements</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/f262b8fecefa8969428de5e37fed01fc.poster.avif?t=1739825521\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326210/extras/f262b8fecefa8969428de5e37fed01fc.webm?t=1739825521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Enjoy! :)</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join our Discord server!</strong></h2><strong></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interesting fact</h2>All art in game was AI-generated (not counting placeholders).",
